{"id":452,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":54,"title":"54. Not So Young","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":10,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/54-not-so-young.452/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/0-54-not-so-young.mp3","transcript":"My son is graduating from high school today!\nAnd my daughter is graduating next year.\nHow old is she?\nShe's sixteen.\nI remember when she was a baby.\nI know. We're getting old.\nDon't say that!\nWhy not? It's true.\nNo, it isn't. We were young when we got married.\nThat's right, but we got married 25 years ago!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:49","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"My son is graduating from high school today!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/1.mp3","time_start":2.68,"time_end":5.59},{"position":2,"content":"And my daughter is graduating next year.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/2.mp3","time_start":5.62,"time_end":8.1},{"position":3,"content":"How old is she?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/3.mp3","time_start":8.1,"time_end":9.08},{"position":4,"content":"She's sixteen.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/4.mp3","time_start":9.08,"time_end":10.28},{"position":5,"content":"I remember when she was a baby.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/5.mp3","time_start":10.36,"time_end":12.38},{"position":6,"content":"I know. We're getting old.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/6.mp3","time_start":12.38,"time_end":14.58},{"position":7,"content":"Don't say that!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/7.mp3","time_start":14.58,"time_end":15.64},{"position":8,"content":"Why not? It's true.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/8.mp3","time_start":15.64,"time_end":17.3},{"position":9,"content":"No, it isn't. We were young when we got married.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/9.mp3","time_start":17.35,"time_end":20.36},{"position":10,"content":"That's right, but we got married 25 years ago!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/54-not-so-young-2022-03-07-21-22-46/10.mp3","time_start":20.44,"time_end":23.72}]}